Info Session.name: Inside GDSC - Connect, Learn, Grow.
Info Session.description: Join us for an insightful info session on GDSC (Google Developer Student Clubs), where we'll delve into the exciting world of technology, learning, and community. Discover how GDSC can empower you to explore new skills, engage with like-minded peers, and excel in your tech journey. Don't miss out on this opportunity to kickstart your path to success!

Cloud.name: Cloud Mastery: Google Cloud Study Jam 2023
Cloud.description: Join us for an immersive learning experience at the Google Cloud Study Jam! Dive into the world of cloud computing with hands-on labs, expert guidance, and interactive sessions. Whether you're a beginner or a cloud enthusiast, this workshop will empower you with the skills and knowledge you need to master Google Cloud Platform. Elevate your cloud IQ and embark on a journey to cloud excellence.
